OL,3,CHindu temple denied capacity increase
OL,4,C- ahead of Diwali
OL,6,FA Hindu temple in Swindon has been
OL,7,Fdenied permission to extend its
OL,8,Fopening hours and capacity- ahead of
OL,9,FDiwali.
OL,11,FSwindon Borough Council offered the
OL,12,Fspace at Wyvern House to the Hindu
OL,13,Fcommunity, after their former place of
OL,14,Fworship was repeatedly targeted by
OL,15,Fthieves and vandals, in incidents
OL,16,Fpolice treated as a 'hate crime.'
OL,18,FThe council has now rejected plans for
OL,19,Fmore than 50 people to attend worship
OL,20,Fat one time - on the grounds of
OL,21,Ftraffic safety concerns.
