OL,6,FWhen the space was approved in 2022,
OL,7,Fit was only allowed to operate between
OL,8,F9.30am to 4pm and 6.30pm to 11pm and
OL,9,Fcapacity was capped.
OL,11,FIssues raised were the impact on roads
OL,12,Fin a busy central area of town, and
OL,13,Fproblems with parking.
OL,15,FThe Hindu Samaj asked for those
OL,16,Frestrictions to be dropped, saying
OL,17,Fmost of its visitors come by foot or
OL,18,Fbus. It added that two weekend events
OL,19,Fper month could attract 150 to 160
OL,20,Fpeople.
