OL,6,FThe council's highways officer, who
OL,7,Fsaid the organisation had not provided
OL,8,Fenough information about the potential
OL,9,Fimpact of larger events, said: "The
OL,10,Fconcern remains that an unrestricted
OL,11,Fpermission may adversely impact on
OL,12,Fpeak-time traffic and local parking as
OL,13,Fa consequence of removing both of
OL,14,Fthese restrictive conditions.
